{"id":1271,"date":"2022-02-25T16:16:00","date_gmt":"2022-02-25T16:16:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/?p=1271"},"modified":"2022-02-23T10:19:23","modified_gmt":"2022-02-23T10:19:23","slug":"change-passwords-and-adjust-password-aging-for-local-user-accounts","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/?p=1271","title":{"rendered":"Change passwords and adjust password aging for local user accounts"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>I don&#8217;t think there is much to explain. You&#8217;ve probably done this task many times before on your PC or phone, but in Linux everything is done over command, so let&#8217;s get right into it. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3>List password information about the user<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">chage -l username<\/pre>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"640\" height=\"143\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-180.png?resize=640%2C143&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1283\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-180.png?w=736&amp;ssl=1 736w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-180.png?resize=300%2C67&amp;ssl=1 300w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-180.png?resize=24%2C5&amp;ssl=1 24w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-180.png?resize=36%2C8&amp;ssl=1 36w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-180.png?resize=48%2C11&amp;ssl=1 48w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Change the password<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>As a simple user without the privileges you can only change your own password but as a root you can change every user password including the root.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">passwd username<\/pre>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"640\" height=\"95\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-181.png?resize=640%2C95&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1284\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-181.png?w=736&amp;ssl=1 736w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-181.png?resize=300%2C44&amp;ssl=1 300w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-181.png?resize=24%2C4&amp;ssl=1 24w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-181.png?resize=36%2C5&amp;ssl=1 36w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-181.png?resize=48%2C7&amp;ssl=1 48w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Adjust password aging <\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Set the maximum number of days during which a password is valid<\/strong> (90 days for example)<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">chage -M 90 username<\/pre>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"640\" height=\"129\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-183.png?resize=640%2C129&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1286\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-183.png?w=879&amp;ssl=1 879w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-183.png?resize=300%2C60&amp;ssl=1 300w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-183.png?resize=768%2C155&amp;ssl=1 768w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-183.png?resize=24%2C5&amp;ssl=1 24w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-183.png?resize=36%2C7&amp;ssl=1 36w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-183.png?resize=48%2C10&amp;ssl=1 48w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Set the minimum number of days between password changes<\/strong> (30 days for example)<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">chage -m 30 username <\/pre>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"640\" height=\"134\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-187.png?resize=640%2C134&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1290\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-187.png?w=883&amp;ssl=1 883w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-187.png?resize=300%2C63&amp;ssl=1 300w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-187.png?resize=768%2C161&amp;ssl=1 768w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-187.png?resize=24%2C5&amp;ssl=1 24w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-187.png?resize=36%2C8&amp;ssl=1 36w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-187.png?resize=48%2C10&amp;ssl=1 48w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>To make user immediately change the password after login<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">chage -d 0 username<\/pre>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-style-default\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"640\" height=\"130\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-182.png?resize=640%2C130&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1285\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-182.png?w=865&amp;ssl=1 865w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-182.png?resize=300%2C61&amp;ssl=1 300w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-182.png?resize=768%2C156&amp;ssl=1 768w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-182.png?resize=24%2C5&amp;ssl=1 24w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-182.png?resize=36%2C7&amp;ssl=1 36w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-182.png?resize=48%2C10&amp;ssl=1 48w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Set expire date<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">chage -E EXPIRE_DATE username<\/pre>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"640\" height=\"127\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-188.png?resize=640%2C127&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1291\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-188.png?w=882&amp;ssl=1 882w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-188.png?resize=300%2C60&amp;ssl=1 300w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-188.png?resize=768%2C152&amp;ssl=1 768w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-188.png?resize=24%2C5&amp;ssl=1 24w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-188.png?resize=36%2C7&amp;ssl=1 36w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/image-188.png?resize=48%2C10&amp;ssl=1 48w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>I don&#8217;t think there is much to explain. You&#8217;ve probably done this task many times [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1305,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"nf_dc_page":"","om_disable_all_campaigns":false,"_mi_skip_tracking":false},"categories":[219],"tags":[460,459,461,98,108,458],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/rhsa-Manage-users-and-groups.png?fit=1280%2C720&ssl=1","_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1271"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/index.php?rest_route=%2Fwp%2Fv2%2Fcomments&post=1271"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"ht